data.description: You wont want to miss this 4 bedroom, turn-of-the-century home in the desirable historic block of beautiful Momence. Located on a corner, double lot with pool and fenced in backyard. This home has 9 ft ceilings on main floor. Many of the rooms have hardwood floors! Living room and foyer have large wooden window seats, both with storage. Home has large wood baseboards throughout. Don't miss the large pocket door between the living room and the office/sitting room!  Freestanding wardrobe in upstairs hallway can stay. TONS of storage! Upstairs bedrooms and hallway have walk-in closets with built-in drawers which offer lots of storage! Laundry room with pantry off kitchen. Home has a full basement with 8 ft ceilings. Two car garage. This home has lots to offer at a reasonable price so call today to set up your showing!
